adage.com/article/cmo-strategy/marvel-s-doctor-strange-drives-a-lamborghini-a-chinese-smartphone/306618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fadage.com%2Farticle%2Fcmo-strategy%2Fmarvel-s-doctor-strange-drives-a-lamborghini-a-chinese-smartphone%2F306618&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=d547d7e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://adage.com/article/cmo-strategy/marvel-s-doctor-strange-drives-a-lamborghini-a-chinese-smartphone/306618</a><br />\n<br />\nThe title character in Marvel's &quot;Doctor Strange&quot; drives (and crashes) a $237,250 Lamborghini Hurac&aacute;n LP610-4. In another twist of product placement, he uses a smartphone from China: It's from Huawei's Honor subbrand, whose flagship phone sells for $399.99."}]}